These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, security-guard
1. the mechanic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Job   | security-guard | mechanic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different pets are kept: lizard, snake
1. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Pet   | lizard | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-3::.
